ement\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a>接口的<code><strong>item()</strong></code>方法返回一个在列表中的索引的项。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>tokenList</var>.item(<var>index</var>)</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"index\"><code><var>index</var></code></dt>\n <dd>&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 类型，一个表示要返回的项的索引。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>类型，一个表示要返回的项。如果数字大于或等于列表的<code>length</code>，则返回<code>null</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在下面的列子中，我们通过<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/classList\"><code>Element.classList</code></a>方法从<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a>元素中获取<code>DOMTokenList</code>对象。 然后使用<code>item(<var>tokenList</var>.length - 1)</code>检索列表中的最后的一个项，并将其写入&lt;span&gt;元素的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>Node.textContent</code></a>。</p>\n\n<p>首先， HTML：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>a b c<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>然后， JavaScript：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> span <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"span\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> classes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> span<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>classList<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> item <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> classes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>classes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nspan<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> item<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>输出结果如下：</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"例子\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/item/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#ref-for-dom-domtokenlist-item①","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.DOMTokenList.item"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DOMTokenList.item","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/item/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"DOMTokenList接口的item()方法返回一个在列表中的索引的项。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DOMTokenList.item()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DOMTokenList.item()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DOMTokenList.item()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/domtokenlist/item","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/domtokenlist/item/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList","title":"DOMTokenList"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList/item","title":"DOMTokenList.item()"}],"pageTitle":"DOMTokenList.item() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}